WEBVTT

00:03:59.993 --> 00:04:05.183
ate and, once tired, he peacefully
went to sleep.

00:04:05.207 --> 00:04:08.503
And the mother kept putting up with it,

00:04:08.527 --> 00:04:12.247
with the problems of both, all alone.

00:04:13.167 --> 00:04:17.423
Another time I heard
one woman tell another

00:04:17.447 --> 00:04:22.623
“In America my son has
to do everything himself,

00:04:22.647 --> 00:04:26.103
now I will have to get him married soon,”

00:04:26.127 --> 00:04:32.223
not conceiving that the son can learn
how to cook and look after himself.